<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">Features:</Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Combine sections from several documents into a single document.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Ability to clone sections, tables, paragraphs etc.,.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Ability to import Contents from one document to another with options similar to Microsoft Word Copy paste functionality. </Paragraph></ListItem></List>

</FlowDocument>
